history record information of the applicant.
(d) Information obtained from the Central Repository under this section:
(1) Is confidential;
(2) May not be redisseminated; and
(3) [Shall] MAY be used only for the licensing purpose authorized by this
title.
(e) The subject of a criminal history records check under this section may contest
the contents of the printed statement issued by the Central Repository as provided in §
